text: From @steveusdin1: Four COVID19 vaccines have reported neutralizing antibody titers from immunized non-human primates. @Novavax had at least an order of magnitude higher titers; but differences in the trial designs can make direct comparisons difficult. https://t.co/57vis1RuDJ https://t.co/lvjqyidMYp
